<file path="README.md">
# SchoolSync V2 üè´

A comprehensive school management system built with React Native and Expo, specifically designed for Indonesian boarding schools (Pesantren). This B2B SaaS solution empowers school management with modern tools to efficiently manage students, teachers, and administrative tasks.

## üåü Features

### üîê Authentication & User Management
- Secure authentication with Supabase
- Role-based access control (Management, Teachers, Students, Parents)
- User onboarding flow with school setup
- Teacher invitation system

### üìä Management Dashboard
- Real-time school statistics and metrics
- Student enrollment tracking
- Teacher management interface
- Subscription and billing overview

### üéì Academic Management
- Student information system
- Class and grade management
- Academic calendar integration
- Performance tracking

### üí∞ Subscription Management
- Tiered pricing plans (Starter, Growing, Enterprise)
- Student count-based billing
- Trial period management
- Payment processing integration

## üõ†Ô∏è Tech Stack

### Frontend
- **React Native** - Cross-platform mobile development
- **Expo** - Development platform and toolchain
- **Expo Router** - File-based navigation
- **TypeScript** - Type-safe development
- **Gluestack UI v2** - Modern component library
- **Tailwind CSS** - Utility-first styling
- **NativeWind** - Tailwind CSS for React Native

### Backend & Database
- **Supabase** - Backend-as-a-Service
- **PostgreSQL** - Relational database
- **Row Level Security (RLS)** - Data security
- **Real-time subscriptions** - Live data updates

### State Management
- **Zustand** - Lightweight state management
- **React Hooks** - Component state management

### Development Tools
- **ESLint** - Code linting
- **Prettier** - Code formatting
- **TypeScript** - Static type checking
- **Metro Bundler** - JavaScript bundler

## üöÄ Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Node.js (v18 or higher)
- npm or yarn
- Expo CLI
- Android Studio (for Android development)
- Xcode (for iOS development, macOS only)

### Installation

1. **Clone the repository**
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/ramdhanhdy/SchoolSyncV2.git
   cd SchoolSyncV2
   ```

2. **Install dependencies**
   ```bash
   npm install
   ```

3. **Set up environment variables**
   ```bash
   cp .env.example .env
   ```
   
   Configure your Supabase credentials:
   ```env
   EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=your_supabase_url
   EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key
   ```

4. **Set up the database**
   - Create a new Supabase project
   - Run the SQL schema from `database/schema.sql`
   - Configure Row Level Security policies

5. **Start the development server**
   ```bash
   npm start
   ```

### Running on Different Platforms

- **Android**: `npm run android`
- **iOS**: `npm run ios`
- **Web**: `npm run web`

## üì± App Structure

```
app/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ (drawer)/           # Main app with drawer navigation
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ (tabs)/         # Tab-based navigation
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ index.tsx       # Dashboard home
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ auth/               # Authentication screens
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ index.tsx       # Auth router
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ onboarding/     # School setup flow
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ _layout.tsx         # Root layout
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ index.tsx           # App entry point

components/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ auth/               # Authentication components
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ onboarding/         # Onboarding flow components
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ ui/                 # Reusable UI components

store/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ authStore.ts        # Authentication state
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ store.ts            # Global state management

utils/
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ supabase.ts         # Supabase client configuration
```

## üóÑÔ∏è Database Schema

The application uses a comprehensive PostgreSQL schema with the following main entities:

- **Schools** - School information and settings
- **Users** - User accounts with role-based access
- **Subscriptions** - Billing and plan management
- **Students** - Student information and enrollment
- **Teachers** - Teacher profiles and assignments
- **Classes** - Class management and scheduling
- **Grades** - Academic performance tracking

## üîß Development

